[metadata]
Name:Offspring keyword creates 1/1 token copy for Thundertrap Trainer
Goal:Win
Turns:5
Difficulty:Easy
Description:Thundertrap Trainer has Offspring {4} — paying {4} additional when casting creates a 1/1 token copy of it when it enters. P0 has 6 mana (Island x3, Plains x3) and casts Thundertrap Trainer ({1}{U}). With 4 mana left after the base cost, the AI pays Offspring, yielding TWO creatures on the battlefield: the original 1/2 Thundertrap Trainer and a 1/1 token copy. P1 has 20 life; P0 wins by attacking with both creatures over multiple turns. If Offspring does NOT fire, P0 has only the 1/2 and cannot win within the turn limit. This is a regression test for mtg-881 wave6 Offspring implementation.

